WELCOME TO GAMMA (Î“)
--------------------

* To open a file(s) press Ctrl+O or click on 'O' on the left side menu.
* To create a new file press Ctrl+N or click on 'N' on the left side menu.
* To open files (recursively) under a directory press Shift+Ctrl+O or click on 'D' on the left side menu.
* Save a file press Ctrl+S or for saving all files click on 'S' on the left side menu.
* Search in a file is placed on top, click on the search icon or press Ctrl+F.
* For advanced search and replace press Ctrl+H or click on 'F' or 'R' on the left side menu.
* For help press F1 or click on 'H' on the left side menu.
* To show information window about Gamma click on 'A' on the left side menu. 
* To open the Welcome page again click on 'W' on the left side menu.


TO MAKE YOUR LIFE EASIER
------------------------
* Press Alt to show the commander window.


